data.description: At almost 3,000 sq ft, this home, built in 2021, has some updates with the future in mind, including the unfinished basement being plumbed for a kitchen and a bathroom. The open concept main floor boasts 9 ft ceilings, kitchen with granite countertops, a dining room, a half bath, and a mudroom off the oversized 2 car garage. Upstairs you will find 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths, one being a jack & jill set up. The loft area is the perfect space for an office, reading nook, or game area. Come warmer weather, the 20x15 patio will be a welcoming spot to relax or entertain. Located in Riverbend at Scioto Landing subdivision and Teays Valley school district.
